{
  "id": "619901ed5219c8001d8ccd19",
  "title": "研究部門の存在意義",
  "created": 1637417459,
  "updated": 1637421584,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "619901ed5219c8001d8ccd19",
      "text": "研究部門の存在意義",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637417459,
      "updated": 1637417462
    },
    {
      "id": "61990ca8aff09e0000e1ab5c",
      "text": "について少し言語化してみる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637420201,
      "updated": 1637420207
    },
    {
      "id": "619904dfaff09e0000e1ab3c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418207,
      "updated": 1637418207
    },
    {
      "id": "6199050caff09e0000e1ab44",
      "text": "「短期的に収入に結びつかない部署」を作るという経営判断は何か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418253,
      "updated": 1637420250
    },
    {
      "id": "6199050eaff09e0000e1ab45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418254,
      "updated": 1637418254
    },
    {
      "id": "619901f6aff09e0000e1ab39",
      "text": "現金というリソースを",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637417463,
      "updated": 1637418279
    },
    {
      "id": "61990526aff09e0000e1ab46",
      "text": "　それよりも良いリソース",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418279,
      "updated": 1637418281
    },
    {
      "id": "6199052aaff09e0000e1ab48",
      "text": "　長期的に価値のあるリソース",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418282,
      "updated": 1637418296
    },
    {
      "id": "61990528aff09e0000e1ab47",
      "text": "　に変えようという経営判断",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418281,
      "updated": 1637418281
    },
    {
      "id": "619904cfaff09e0000e1ab3b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418191,
      "updated": 1637418191
    },
    {
      "id": "61990507aff09e0000e1ab3f",
      "text": "研究テーマがトップダウンで与えられる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418247,
      "updated": 1637418363
    },
    {
      "id": "6199062daff09e0000e1ab4a",
      "text": "→現金を特定ドメインの知識に変換しようとしている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418541,
      "updated": 1637418564
    },
    {
      "id": "61990507aff09e0000e1ab40",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418247,
      "updated": 1637418247
    },
    {
      "id": "61990647aff09e0000e1ab4b",
      "text": "テーマがトップダウンで与えられない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418568,
      "updated": 1637420335
    },
    {
      "id": "619906adaff09e0000e1ab4d",
      "text": "→「どのドメインの知識が有益であるか(=テーマ)の探索」を研究者に委譲している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418670,
      "updated": 1637420358
    },
    {
      "id": "619907d5aff09e0000e1ab50",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418965,
      "updated": 1637418965
    },
    {
      "id": "61990940aff09e0000e1ab53",
      "text": "別の言い方",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637419329,
      "updated": 1637419331
    },
    {
      "id": "61990648aff09e0000e1ab4c",
      "text": "現金を研究者の可処分時間に変換する経営判断であって、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418568,
      "updated": 1637420393
    },
    {
      "id": "61990d69aff09e0000e1ab5d",
      "text": "その判断は研究者がその可処分時間を「より価値の高いもの」に変換することを期待して行われている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637420393,
      "updated": 1637420405
    },
    {
      "id": "61990d76aff09e0000e1ab5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637420406,
      "updated": 1637420406
    },
    {
      "id": "619907f9aff09e0000e1ab52",
      "text": "「なにが価値の高いものか」という判断軸は天下りで与えれられない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637419001,
      "updated": 1637419047
    },
    {
      "id": "61990d83aff09e0000e1ab5f",
      "text": "それはつまり",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637420419,
      "updated": 1637420422
    },
    {
      "id": "61990746aff09e0000e1ab4e",
      "text": "何に変換するかは研究者個人の判断に任されている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418822,
      "updated": 1637418908
    },
    {
      "id": "6199078faff09e0000e1ab4f",
      "text": "変換した産物がどうして価値があるのかを言語化するのは研究者個人の責任である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418895,
      "updated": 1637419281
    },
    {
      "id": "619907dbaff09e0000e1ab51",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418972,
      "updated": 1637418972
    },
    {
      "id": "61990dd2aff09e0000e1ab60",
      "text": "この状況で「変換した産物は現金です」と言われるとモヤモヤする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637420499,
      "updated": 1637420643
    },
    {
      "id": "61990de5aff09e0000e1ab61",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637420522,
      "updated": 1637420522
    },
    {
      "id": "619910e3aff09e0000e1ab62",
      "text": "週次では粒度が細かすぎるからやらないけど",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637421284,
      "updated": 1637421359
    },
    {
      "id": "6199120faff09e0000e1ab66",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637421584,
      "updated": 1637421584
    },
    {
      "id": "6199113eaff09e0000e1ab64",
      "text": "成果の説明",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637421375,
      "updated": 1637421380
    },
    {
      "id": "6199114aaff09e0000e1ab65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637421386,
      "updated": 1637421386
    },
    {
      "id": "61991107aff09e0000e1ab63",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637421320,
      "updated": 1637421320
    },
    {
      "id": "6199094daff09e0000e1ab54",
      "text": "リソースに関しては一般的に「必要になったときに市場調達する」という選択肢がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637419341,
      "updated": 1637419737
    },
    {
      "id": "61990adaaff09e0000e1ab57",
      "text": "知識に関しては例えば「ある知識ドメインが必要になったときに外部からコンサルタントを雇う」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637419739,
      "updated": 1637419770
    },
    {
      "id": "61990a7eaff09e0000e1ab56",
      "text": "このとき",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637419646,
      "updated": 1637419835
    },
    {
      "id": "61990b3baff09e0000e1ab58",
      "text": "　そもそもそんなコンサルタントがいるのか？という不確実性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637419835,
      "updated": 1637419851
    },
    {
      "id": "61990b4eaff09e0000e1ab59",
      "text": "　適切なコンサルタントを探すコスト",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637419854,
      "updated": 1637419864
    },
    {
      "id": "61990b58aff09e0000e1ab5a",
      "text": "　そのコンサルタントが社内の文脈を理解してないことによって発生するマイナス",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637419864,
      "updated": 1637419945
    },
    {
      "id": "61990ba9aff09e0000e1ab5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637419946,
      "updated": 1637419947
    },
    {
      "id": "61990500aff09e0000e1ab3e",
      "text": "どう結びつくのか不明な",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418240,
      "updated": 1637418240
    },
    {
      "id": "6199056aaff09e0000e1ab49",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1637418346,
      "updated": 1637418346
    }
  ]
}